## 📝 Update & Maintenance

```bash
# Most updates are automatic via symlinks
# Just restart Claude Code after editing agents/commands

# For Python skills updates:
./update.sh skills

# Full system update:
./update.sh all
```

## 🆘 Getting Help

- **In-session:** `/ask-specialist [question]` or `/check-understanding [topic]`
- **Documentation:** See [COMMANDS_README.md](./COMMANDS_README.md) for detailed command reference
- **Specialists:** Review `agents/` folder for available experts
- **Issues:** Check existing documentation in `docs/`

